osely monitored for emergent symptoms of CNS toxicity for two weeks (five weeks if fluoxetine was taken) or until 24 hours after the last dose of linezolid, whichever comes first. Patients and/or their caregivers should be advised to seek medical attention if potential symptoms of serotonin syndrome develop. Treatment with the MAOI may be resumed 24 hours after the last dose of linezolid.', 'Synergism', NULL, NULL, 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', 1767317476);
